title: when the final boss is a random encounter

media:group.media:title: when the final boss is a random encounter
media:group.media:description:
Guide for the fight:
Klu Klux Grand Dragon has 99% chance to shadow counter. One shot spells do not one shot him. Dragon man is from the south so the biscuit that comes with the 2 piece combo is dry. Do not let Dragon man touch the little boy. He is a Mishima. Adds spawn after the 2nd turn. Shrek will pull your party's agro while SpongeBob provides vaporize reaction with Hu Tao. If you make it to the 5th turn, General Shepherd spawns to one shot. Chance of Low Tier God spawning to provoke you into a party wipe. Johnny Sins should be casted in a live action One Punch Man as Saitama.
